Description: The overall goal of the `TADAShinyAnalyze` shiny app is to
    provide a third module to the `TADAShiny` shiny app where users can
    complete batch and custom analyses by monitoring locations or
    assessment units (AUs) with the ultimate goal of supporting water
    quality management.
